<H3> <TI>   Colonel Matalon Takes Over as 5th Brigade Commander </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  PY0501202594 </F>
<F P=103> PY0501202594 </F>
<F P=104></F>



<TEXT>
Article   Type:BFN 

  [Editorial Report] San Miguel de Tucuman LA GAZETA in 
Spanish on page 12 of its 11 December 1993 issue reports that 
Colonel Carlos Roberto Matalon was installed as 5th Mechanized 
Brigade commander, replacing General Rafael Alberto Cazaux. The 
ceremony was held at the Gregorio Araoz de la Madrid Military 
