<F P=100> MEXICO </F>
<H3> <TI>   Attack on Mexican Consulate in El Paso </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  PA0401132194 Mexico City XEW Television Network in Spanish 
1200 GMT 4 Jan 94 </F>

<F P=103> PA0401132194 </F>
<F P=104>  Mexico City XEW Television Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Spanish </F>
Article Type:BFN 

<F P=106> [From the "Echo" newscast] </F>
  [Text] The Mexican Foreign Relations Secretariat has 
reported in a communique that a group of unidentified persons 
attacked the Mexican Consulate in the U.S. city of El Paso on 3 
January. According to the communique, the attack took place in 
the early hours of 3 January when some unidentified persons 
hurled a rock and a Molotov cocktail inside the Consulate. 
Fortunately, no injuries were reported and material damage was 
minimal. A similar incident took place at the same Consulate a 
year ago. 

</TEXT>

