<F P=102>  PA0901205494 Santa Fe de Bogota Inravision Television Cadena 
1 in Spanish 1806 GMT 9 Jan 94 </F>

<F P=103> PA0901205494 </F>
<F P=104>  Santa Fe de Bogota Inravision Television Cadena 
