<F P=100> Venezuela </F>
<H3> <TI>   Caracas Reports Helicopter Crash </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  PA0801015694 Caracas Venezolana de Television Network in 
Spanish 2350 GMT 7 Jan 94 </F>

<F P=103> PA0801015694 </F>
<F P=104>  Caracas Venezolana de Television Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Spanish </F>
Article Type:BFN 

<F P=106> [From "The News" newscast] </F>
  [Text] Two members of the National Guard were injured when 
a helicopter of the Armed Forces of National Cooperation went 
down in near Cutufi. The helicopter's tail rotor failed and the 
pilot had to make an emergency landing near the 
Colombian-Venezuelan border. High-ranking officers of Regional 
Command No.1 went to the area to learn the details of the 
accident. 

</TEXT>

</DOC>

